    id: 'prompt-48',
    prompt: 'Create a daily ritual or memorial practice that honors your loved one and helps you feel connected to their memory',
    category: 'action',
    helpText: 'Establishing a meaningful daily practice provides structure and comfort while creating an ongoing way to honor your loved one\'s memory as part of your healing process. This could include lighting a candle each morning, visiting their photo and sharing something about your day, writing a brief note in a memorial journal, or listening to a song that reminds you of them. Choose something that feels authentic to your relationship and can be realistically maintained, allowing this ritual to become a source of comfort and connection rather than an additional burden during your grief journey.'
